<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="pt-br"> <head> <meta charset="utf-8"> <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"> <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/GGBGGHJGDGPGOG> <title> Portal de Acesso Remoto </title> <style> body{ margin:0} *{ -webkit-box-sizing:border-box; -moz-box-sizing:border-box; box-sizing:border-box} html{ font-size:10px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent} body{ font-family:"Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:1.42857143; color:#333; background-color:#fff} .carousel-inner>.item>a>img,.carousel-inner>.item>img,.img-responsive{ display:block; max-width:100%; height:auto} .container{ padding-right:15px; padding-left:15px; margin-right:auto; margin-left:auto} @media (min-width:768px){ .container{ width:750px} } @media (min-width:992px){ .container{ width:970px} } @media (min-width:1200px){ .container{ width:1170px} } .col-sm-4,.col-sm-8{ position:relative; min-height:1px; padding-right:15px; padding-left:15px} @media (min-width:768px){ .col-sm-4,.col-sm-8{ float:left} .col-sm-8{ width:66.66666667%} .col-sm-4{ width:33.33333333%} } .btn{ display:inline-block; padding:6px 12px; margin-bottom:0; font-size:14px; font-weight:400; line-height:1.42857143; text-align:center; white-space:nowrap; vertical-align:middle; cursor:pointer; border:1px solid transparent; border-radius:4px} .clearfix:after,.clearfix:before,.row:after,.row:before{ display:table; content:" "} .btn-group-vertical>.btn-group:after,.btn-toolbar:after,.clearfix:after{ clear:both} .pull-left{ float:left!important} </style> <style> *{ border:0; font:"Courier New",Courier,monospace} html{ position:relative; min-height:100%} body{ background-color:#e0e2e9; font-family:Arial,Helvetica,Verdana,"Bitstream Vera Sans",sans-serif; line-height:150%; margin-bottom:80px} .topo{ width:100%; height:auto; margin:0 auto; padding:0; background-image:url(/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/CGHGPFJGOGEHCHPG); background-repeat:repeat-x; background-position:left} .topo .centroTopo{ height:auto; margin:auto 30%; padding:0; background-image:url(/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/IGFGBGEG); background-repeat:no-repeat} body>.container{ padding-top:80px} b{ justify-content:center; text-align:center; display:block; font-size:3rem; padding:30px} .inputs{ justify-content:center; text-align:center; display:block} .inputs input{ width:180px; height:30px; border:1px solid #2e2b2b; padding:5px; margin:5px} .botao{ justify-content:center; text-align:center; display:block; padding-top:1rem; padding-bottom:3rem} .botao button{ background-color:#3c926f; color:#fff} .botao button:hover{ background-color:#41a97f; color:#fff} .dicas{ justify-content:center; text-align:center; display:block; padding-bottom:.3rem; font-weight:700; font-size:medium} .container{ width:870px; background:#f6f5f5; border-radius:20px; cursor:pointer; box-shadow:0 0 10px 5px #d0d0d0; margin-bottom:3rem} .conteudo{ padding:25px} .info{ display:flex; padding-bottom:1.7rem} .info img{ width:28px} .info p{ display:flex; margin-left:10px; align-self:center; margin:auto; line-height:1.6rem; color:#000} .info p:nth-child(2n){ display:flex; margin-left:10px; align-self:center; line-height:1.6rem} section{ display:block} .footer{ position:absolute; bottom:0; background-color:#fff; background-repeat:repeat-x; background-position:left; width:100%; color:#143f6c; font-size:12px; height:80px} .rodape{ background:#fff; border-top:5px solid #143f6c} .rodape .gap-right{ margin-right:15px} .col-sm-4 sti-info{ position:relative; min-height:1px; padding-right:15px; padding-left:15px; width:33.33333333%} .rodape .sti-info img{ float:right; margin-top:8px} .col-sm-8{ width:66.66666667%} @media (max-width:540px){ .footer{ font-size:8px} .topo .centroTopo{ margin:auto} .container .row h3{ font-size:20px} .container .row h4{ font-size:15px} } @media (min-width:540px) and (max-width:768px){ .footer{ font-size:8px} .topo .centroTopo{ margin:auto} .container .row h3{ font-size:22px} .container .row h4{ font-size:16px} } @media (min-width:768px) and (max-width:992px){ .footer{ font-size:10px} .topo .centroTopo{ margin:auto 10%} .container .row h3{ font-size:24px} .container .row h4{ font-size:18px} } a{ display: contents; } </style> <!--[if lt IE 9]><script nonce="Bo7zgrXbH" src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/html5shiv/3.7.0/html5shiv.js"></script><script nonce="THjpOIQ34" src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/respond.js/1.3.0/respond.min.js"></script><![endif]--> </head> <body> <main class="principal"> <div class="topo"> <div class="centroTopo"> <img class="img-responsive" src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/FHGGCGBGNCMGPGHGPGNCFGNCCGCHBGDHBGPG alt="Universidade Federal da Bahia"/> </div> </div> <b> Portal de Acesso Remoto </b> <!-- Inputs - colocar as caracteristicas do atual --> <form class="prompt" action="/remote/logincheck" method="post" name="f" autocomplete="off"> <div class="inputs"> <!--remoteauthtimeout=10-->
<input type="text" name="username" id="username" placeholder="Name"><input type="password" name="credential" id="credential" placeholder="Password" maxlength="128"><div class="info-message" id="token_msg" style="display: none;"><div class="message-content" id="token_label"></div></div><input type="password" style="display: none;" maxlength="128" name="credential2" id="credential2"><input type="password" style="display: none;" maxlength="128" name="credential3" id="credential3"><div class="button-actions wide"><button class="primary" type="button" name="ftm_push_button" id="ftm_push_button" onclick="try_ftm_push()    " style="display: none" disabled>Use FTM Push</button></div><input type="password" style="display: none;" placeholder="Token" name="code" id="code"><div id="driftmsg" style="display: none;" class="warning-message">Token clock drift detected. Please input the next code and continue.</div><input type="password" style="display: none;" name="code2" id="code2" placeholder="Next Token Code"> <!--<input type="text" name="username" id="username" placeholder="Name"><input type="password" name="credential" id="credential" placeholder="Password" maxlength="128">--> </div> <div class="botao"> <button class="primary btn btn-primary" type="button" name="login_button" id="login_button" onClick="try_login()"> Login </button> <button type="button" name="skip_button" id="skip_button" onClick="try_skip()" style="display:none"> Skip </button> </div> </form> <p class="dicas"> DICAS DE SEGURANÇA </p> <!-- Cards --> <div class="container"> <div class="conteudo"> <div class="info"> <img src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/HHJGGGJG alt="wifi"/> <p> Não se conecte em outra rede wi-fi que não seja a sua. </p> </div> <div class="info"> <img src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/DGBGEGFGBGEGPG alt="cadeado"/> <p> Evite deixar seu computador aberto, mesmo que travado. Se não estiver usando, desligue-o ou coloque-o em stand-by. </p> </div> <div class="info"> <img src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/CHFGMGPGBGEG alt="reload"/> <p> Mantenha seu Sistema Operacional e Antivírus sempre atualizados. </p> </div> <div class="info"> <img src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/AHBGDHEHBG alt="pasta"/> <p> Documentos de Trabalho devem ser compartilhados apenas no ambiente institucional. Mais informações sobre compartilhamento de arquivos, consulte o manual de uso. </p> </div> <div class="info"> <img src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/EHFGMGFGGGPGOGFG alt="telefone"> <p> Ligações e conferências com colegas e clientes devem ser realizadas em ambientes controlados. </p> </div> <div class="info"> <img src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/IGBGDGLGFGCH alt="hacker"> <p> Tenha cuidado extra com mensagens maliciosas (spam e phishing). </p> </div> <div class="info"> <img src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/DGFGMGFHMGBGCHNCOGBGNCNGBGPG alt="celular-na-mao"> <p> Ao acessar de dispositivos móveis, amplie os cuidados com o acesso ao aparelho. </p> </div> <div class="info"> <img src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/EGPGHHOGMGPGBGEG alt="download"> <p> Evite baixar arquivos no computador pessoal, pen-drives e hd's externos. </p> </div> </div> </div> <p class="dicas"> DICAS DE USO </p> <div class="container"> <div class="conteudo"> <div class="info"> <img src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/NGBGOGFHBGMG alt="manual"/> <p> <a href="https://sti.ufba.br/sites/cpd.ufba.br/files/manual-portal-de-acessoremoto_0.pdf" target="_blank"> Manual do Portal de Acesso Remoto. </a> </p> </div> <div class="info"> <img src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/FGDHDGFHEGPG alt="escudo"/> <p> O acesso ao <a href="https://www.periodicos.capes.gov.br" target="_blank" > Portal de Periódicos da CAPES </a> deve ser realizado diretamente através de autenticação federada (CAFe), sem a necessidade de acesso a este portal. </p> </div> <div class="info"> <img src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/AHBGHGJGOGBGNCHHFGCG alt="pagina-web"/> <p> O acesso ao Portal IEEE Xplore deve ser realizado por meio deste Portal de Acesso Remoto, através do endereço disponível após autenticação. </p> </div> </div> </div> <p class="dicas"> </p> <!-- RODAPE --> </main> <footer class="footer"> <div class="rodape"> <section id="block-block-9" class="block block-block clearfix"> <div class="col-sm-8 clearfix ufba-info"> <img alt="brasao-ufba" class="pull-left gap-right" src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/CGCHBGDHBGPGNCFHGGCGBG> STI - SUPERINTENDÊNCIA DE TECNOLOGIA DA INFORMAÇÃO <br/> Avenida Milton Santos, s/n - Campus de Ondina CEP 40.170-110 Salvador-Bahia <br/> Telefone: 71 3283-6124 <br/> </div> <div class="col-sm-4 sti-info"> <img alt="sti-logo" class="" src=/XX/YY/ZZ/CI/DHEHJGNCMGPGHGPG> </div> </section> </div> </footer> </body> <input type=hidden name="ftm_push_enabled" id="ftm_push_enabled" value="1"><input type=hidden name=just_logged_in value=1><input type=hidden name=magic id=magic_id value=""><input type=hidden name=reqid id=reqid_id value="0"><input type=hidden name=grpid id=grpid_id value=""><input type=hidden name=realm id=realm_id value=""><input type=hidden name=redir value="/sslvpn/portal/index.html"><input type=hidden name=saml_login id=saml_login_id value="0"><script type="text/javascript" src="/js/legacy_theme_setup.js"></script><script type="text/javascript" src="/sslvpn/js/login.js "></script><script type="text/javascript" src="/remote/fgt_lang?lang=en"></script><script>document.onkeydown = key_pressdown;function load_login_strings() {var tmp = document.getElementById("err_val");var name = document.getElementById("username");var pass = document.getElementById("credential");if (tmp) {tmp.innerHTML = fgt_lang["error"] + ": " + fgt_lang[tmp.getAttribute('title')];}name.placeholder = fgt_lang["Username"];pass.placeholder = fgt_lang["sslvpn_portal::Password"];}window.onload = load_login_strings;</script></html>
